			>
				<img
					width="1553"
					height="873"
					src="/assets/at-work.jpg"
					alt="Antonio Molina at work with a colleague"
				/>
			</Hero>

			<section>
				<h2 class="section-title">Background</h2>
				<div class="content">
					<p>
						<strong>Mechanical Engineering & Design:</strong> Strong foundation in mechanical design principles, with hands-on experience in industrial and steelmaking environments.
					</p>
					<p>
						<strong>CAD & 3D Modeling:</strong> Proficient in Autodesk Inventor for mechanical drawing, assembly modeling, and 3D visualization.
					</p>
