						pretium fusce.
					</p>
				</div>
			</section>
			<section>
				<h2 class="section-title">Education</h2>
				<div class="content">
					<h5>Iron & Steel Specialist Degree</h5>
					<p>IAS (Instituto Argentino de Siderúrgia)</p>
					<p><em>Mar 2019 - Mar 2021 / Buenos Aires, Argentina</em></p>
				</div>
				<div class="content">
